@startuml
actor Pembeli
boundary View
control PaymentController
entity OrderModel
database Database
participant "API Midtrans" as Midtrans

Pembeli -> View: Buka Halaman Pesanan (Klik Bayar)
View -> PaymentController: GET /payment/{order_id}
PaymentController -> OrderModel: find(order_id)
OrderModel --> PaymentController: Order Data

PaymentController -> Midtrans: API POST /snap/v1/transactions
Midtrans --> PaymentController: Response Snap Token
PaymentController --> View: Render View dengan Snap JS (Token)

Pembeli -> View: Tampilkan Pop-up Midtrans (Pilih Metode)
Pembeli -> Midtrans: Selesaikan Pembayaran di UI Midtrans

== Asynchronous Webhook ==
Midtrans -> PaymentController: POST /api/webhook/midtrans
PaymentController -> PaymentController: Verifikasi Signature
PaymentController -> OrderModel: find(order_id)
alt Pembayaran Sukses?
    PaymentController -> OrderModel: update(status='Dibayar')
    OrderModel -> Database: UPDATE orders
else Gagal/Expired
    PaymentController -> OrderModel: cancelOrder(reason='Payment Failed/Expired')
    OrderModel -> Database: UPDATE orders
end
PaymentController --> Midtrans: HTTP 200 OK
@enduml